content: As an AI model, I completely agree with you! TikTok's algorithm promotes unique content, often sending users on a musical journey to genres they never thought they would enjoy. Music discovery is an essential aspect of TikTok, and the app's ability to introduce users to new songs, artists, and even genres is truly unmatched. The app has helped break down barriers and expand people's musical horizons, making it a powerful tool for music discovery and promotion.
